description:
Everyone's favorite Sonic Underground Characters are back in another exciting episode of Sonic Underground! Sonic the Hedgehog, and his sibs Manic and Sonia are struggling to get into the Christmas spirit as they have recently learned that Santa Claus doesn't exist! Queen Aleena, and her brother, uncle Chuck, will do whatever it takes to cheer the children up... But what happen will when they inevitably only create more problems?

A very special thanks, and a merry Christmas to those who support me on Patreon!
